and empowerment.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to cultural performances and insightful interactions between TPSODL leadership and the school community, the event served as a platform for shared learning and fostering deeper connections between volunteers and students.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simultaneously, TPSODL organised a free eye check-up camp at the School for Visually Impaired in Koraput, offering essential health services to students.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koraput\", \"score\": 0.9999813726901764, \"rank\": 1.8627656837930505e-05, \"text\": \"Koraput\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koraput\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koraput\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on the occasion, Garg said, \\\"We are proud to kick off the 22nd edition of Tata Volunteering Week with a series of impactful and inspiring events.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tata_Consultancy_Services\", \"score\": 0.9956965623741009, \"rank\": 0.004189764082415227, \"text\": \"Tata\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tata_Consultancy_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tata_Consultancy_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The theme perfectly reflects the company's mission to unite and empower communities by promoting inclusivity, skill development, and healthcare support.\\\"\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ARINDAM GANGULY, OP  Enter your email to get our daily news in your inbox.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click Here: Plastic Free Odisha                                                              And